<font color="#ffffff">I'm okay.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

266
00:24:13,760 --> 00:24:15,520
<font color="#ffffff">Promise me you won't fall asleep.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

267
00:24:15,600 --> 00:24:17,000
<font color="#ffffff">Don't fall asleep, Jay.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

268
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:18,720
<font color="#ffffff">Don't fall asleep.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

269
00:24:18,800 --> 00:24:20,200
<font color="#ffffff">Don't fall asleep!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

270
00:24:20,280 --> 00:24:23,400
<font color="#ffffff">Yes, calm down, Fai.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

271
00:24:23,480 --> 00:24:25,200
